# Changelog

All notable changes to the War Commanders Automation Tool will be documented in this file.

## [Unreleased]
### Added
- Initial project structure with modular design
- Core functionality for macro recording and playback
- Basic GUI interface with Tkinter
- Security module for credential management
- Multi-account support with encryption
- Automatic updates system
- Backup and restore functionality

### Changed
- Optimized module loading for better performance
- Improved error handling and logging
- Enhanced GUI responsiveness

### Fixed
- Fixed package dependency detection
- Resolved tab switching lag issues
- Fixed potential memory leaks in GUI

## [0.1.0] - 2025-07-23
### Added
- Initial release of War Commanders Automation Tool
- Basic macro recording and playback functionality
- Simple command-line interface
- Basic error handling
